Solution: It is crucial to address the patient's inquiry about fluid intake by emphasizing the importance of following a prescribed fluid restriction to prevent exacerbation of heart failure symptoms. Encourage her to track her daily fluid intake and discuss any concerns or difficulties she may have in adhering to the recommendations.

